<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <!--head area where style sheet is linked and title writen-->
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/css/materialize.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Staff Maker</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="navbar-fixed">
        <nav>
            <div class="nav-wrapper teal accent-3">
                <a href="#!" class="brand-logo left">TekTalk</a>
                <ul class="right">
                    <li><a href="sass.html">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="badges.html">Dashboard</a></li>
                    <li><a href="badges.html">Log Out</a></li>
                    <li><a href="badges.html">Log In</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- this is the main post template -->
        <div id="flow-text" class="center card-panel">
            <h4 id="flow-text" class="white-text center card-panel pink lighten-4">
                Title
            </h4>
            <p class="flow-text">
                One common flaw we've seen in many frameworks is a lack of support for truly responsive text. While
                elements
                on the page resize fluidly, text still resizes on a fixed basis. To ameliorate this problem, for text
                heavy
                pages, we've created a class that fluidly scales text size and line-height to optimize readability for
                the
                user. Line length stays between 45-80 characters and line height scales to be larger on smaller screens.
            </p>
            <p class="flow-text">
                Posted by: User123 at 5:30 PM 6/6/06
            </p>
            <a id="updateBtn" class="grey-text waves-effect waves-light btn light-blue lighten-4">Update</a>
            <a id="deleteBtn" class="grey-text waves-effect waves-light btn  purple lighten-4">Delete</a>
        </div>
        <!-- this is the template for the dashboard post selection -->
        <div class="center card-panel grey lighten-2">
            <a id="dashboardPostName" class="waves-effect waves-teal btn-flat grey darken-2 white-text">
                Post Name 6/6/06
            </a>
        </div>
        <!-- this is the template for the form element that takes in new posts -->
        <div id="flow-text" class="center card-panel">
            <h5 id="flow-text" class="white-text center card-panel pink lighten-4">
                New Post
            </h5>

            <div class="row">
                <form class="col s12">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="active input-field col s6">
                            <input id="input_text" type="text" data-length="10">
                            <label class="active" for="input_text">Post Title</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="active input-field col s12">
                            <textarea id="textarea2" class="materialize-textarea" data-length="120"></textarea>
                            <label class="active" for="textarea2">Post Content</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a id="submitPostBtn" class="waves-effect waves-teal btn-flat">
                        SUBMIT
                    </a>
                </form>
            </div>

        </div>
        <!-- this is the element for updating posts -->
        <div id="flow-text" class="center card-panel">
            <h5 id="flow-text" class="grey-text center card-panel light-blue lighten-4">
                Update Post
            </h5>

            <div class="row">
                <form class="col s12">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="active input-field col s6">
                            <input id="input_text" type="text" data-length="10">
                            <label class="active" for="input_text">Post Title</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="active input-field col s12">
                            <textarea id="textarea2" class="materialize-textarea" data-length="120"></textarea>
                            <label class="active" for="textarea2">Post Content</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a id="updatePostBtn" class="waves-effect waves-teal btn-flat">
                        UPDATE
                    </a>
                </form>
            </div>

        </div>
        <!-- this is the template for a new comment  -->
        <div id="flow-text" class="center card-panel">
            <h5 id="flow-text" class="white-text center card-panel pink lighten-4">
                New Comment
            </h5>

            <div class="row">
                <form class="col s12">

                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="active input-field col s12">
                            <textarea id="textarea2" class="materialize-textarea" data-length="120"></textarea>
                            <label class="active" for="textarea2">Comment Text</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a id="newCmtSubmitBtn" class="waves-effect waves-teal btn-flat">
                        SUBMIT
                    </a>
                </form>
            </div>

        </div>
        <!-- this is the template to a finished comment -->
        <div class="center card-panel purple lighten-4">
            <p class="flow-text">
                This is a great post thank you so much for posting it!
            </p>
            <p class="flow-text purple-text">
                User123 on 6/6/06
            </p>
        </div>
        <!-- this is the template for the login -->
        <div id="flow-text" class="center card-panel">
            <h4 id="flow-text" class="white-text center card-panel cyan accent-3">
                Login
            </h4>

            <div class="row ">
                <form class="col s12">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="active input-field col s6">
                            <input id="input_text" type="text" data-length="20">
                            <label class="active" for="input_text">username</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="active input-field col s6 ">
                            <input id="input_text" type="text" data-length="20">
                            <label class="active" for="input_text">password</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a id="loginSubmitBtn" class="waves-effect waves-teal btn-flat">
                        Log In
                    </a>
                    <a id="goToSignUpBtn" class="waves-effect waves-teal btn-flat">
                        Sign Up Instead
                    </a>
                </form>
            </div>

        </div>
        <!-- this is the template for the sign up section -->
        <div id="flow-text" class="center card-panel">
            <h4 id="flow-text" class="white-text center card-panel  amber lighten-3">
                Sign Up
            </h4>

            <div class="row ">
                <form class="col s12">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="active input-field col s6">
                            <input id="input_text" type="text" data-length="20">
                            <label class="active" for="input_text">username</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row ">
                        <div class="active input-field col s6">
                            <input id="input_text" type="text" data-length="20">
                            <label class="active" for="input_text">email address</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="active input-field col s6 ">
                            <input id="input_text" type="text" data-length="20">
                            <label class="active" for="input_text">password</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a id="loginSubmitBtn" class="waves-effect waves-teal btn-flat">
                        Log In
                    </a>
                    <a id="goToSignInBtn" class="waves-effect waves-teal btn-flat">
                        Sign In Instead
                    </a>
                </form>
            </div>

        </div>
        <!-- floating new note button -->
        <div class="fixed-action-btn">
            <a class="btn-floating btn-large teal accent-3">
              <i class="large material-icons">mode_edit</i>
            </a>
           
          </div>
                

    </div>


</body>

</html>